#Remove the bonds of affection <BR> as one might pluck an autumn flower. <BR> Walk the Way that leads to liberation <BR> explained by the Awakened One.|XX. THE PATH 285
#It is a fool <BR> who indulges in dreaming <BR> about the most comfortable <BR> place to live, saying<BR> "here it will be warm,<BR> there it will be cool" -<BR> unaware of impending death.|XX. THE PATH 286
