#It is hard to live <BR> the life of renunciation;<BR> its challenges <BR> are difficult to find pleasant.<BR> Yet it is also hard to live <BR> the householder's life;<BR> there is pain <BR> when associating with those <BR> among whom one feels no companionship.<BR> To wander uncommitted <BR> is always going to be difficult;<BR> why not renounce<BR> the deluded pursuit of pain?|XI. VARIOUS 302
