#Accumulated sadness,<BR> troubled sleep,<BR> blame and remorse<BR> are an adulterer's lot.|XXII. HELL 309
#Brief is the delight<BR> of the fearful, adulterous couple,<BR> for only painful consequences can follow. |XXII. HELL 310
